Additionally, the paper involves the study of graph classes such as threshold graphs, colored trees, and paths, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.CG (Computational Geometry). Finally, the paper also involves some combinatorial aspects, which could place it under cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
